      "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review+1\n\nThis patch significantly changes (and improves) the way unreplied requests are tracked compared to what is described in the LU-5319 design.\n\nIt might be useful to write in a small design document, how the imp_unreplied_list/imp_known_replied_xid/rq_last_xid fields are managed, especially during the recovery phase.",
